        {
            "title": "廣末涼子被捕︱禁戴bra每周沖涼一次  拘留生活曝光",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"廣末涼子4月8日因襲擊醫護人員，涉嫌傷害罪被捕。IG@ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/60bd1a838d569f3649046f78b6a76252/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041322581674009.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">廣末涼子4月8日因襲擊醫護人員，涉嫌傷害罪被捕。IG@ryoko_hirosue_official</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>日本女星廣末涼子4月8日因襲擊醫護人員，涉嫌傷害罪被捕。檢察方上周四（10日）獲法院批准，羈押廣末至少10日，預計關至周六（19日）。廣末涼子的律師提出準抗告，遭另一名法官駁回。日媒報道，11日曾有一名女性造訪拘留所，疑為廣末的親人。另外，有警界人士披露廣末涼子拘留所生活的數個禁忌，例如原子筆要向所方借用、Bra屬於危險物等。\n\n</p><h2>Bra被視為危險物</h2>\n<p>警界人士表示，在拘留所中，牙刷、毛巾及肥皂等個人生活用品，均需自費購買，親友探訪時大多是送現金、衣服及筆記本，但有繩子的物品被視為違禁品，例如連帽上衣、抽繩運動褲等，以防被用來自殺。Bra也被列為危險物，所有羈押者進入拘留所後均會被沒收Bra。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3445991/\">廣末涼子被捕｜涉踢傷護士 被裁定拘留10天</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2f98c3905c4fca43a1bd5ebd61b6770/2025-04/461241659_1508028216362984_1365953756481588892_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/821413caf0d3d8ae97a551d0acf4ab60/2025-04/465458072_1086852193063954_757863287248807693_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"廣末涼子車禍送院襲擊醫護被捕。日本女星廣末涼子。IG＠ryoko_hirosue_official \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0eb56986688a3efeeb68a85d2fd2dfe7/2025-04/New_Project_-_2025-04-09T122610_642.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廣末涼子車禍送院襲擊醫護被捕。日本女星廣末涼子。IG＠ryoko_hirosue_official \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/539efbab442ed74c88b9cff541de7d47/2025-04/472930378_895808766078309_4005445351994631318_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d1a23ed644f2f5b052e52d8bfc14163/2025-04/472539732_1628951594361122_1937176176290120587_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9fb732a31d0d591daa493829d9daaa52/2025-04/485060843_17900239905150686_3337390332944625420_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a69679927a467a7de1000f0f160540f/2025-04/468374947_564185106234797_1786166933560601126_n_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日本女星廣末涼子。instagram.com/ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"廣末涼子4月8日因襲擊醫護人員，涉嫌傷害罪被捕。IG@ryoko_hirosue_official\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/834aa3a0e80deb182916afe1c08bee6f/2025-04/Best_Day_Ever_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廣末涼子4月8日因襲擊醫護人員，涉嫌傷害罪被捕。IG@ryoko_hirosue_official\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>此外，尖形原子筆亦不准接收，但在拘留所內可申請租借原子筆，每支筆帶有編號，會限制借出時間。\n\n</p>\n<p>警界人士還透露了羈押者的沖涼時間，「基本上一星期一次，夏天改成一星期兩次，（廣末）這次應該是一星期洗一次」。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3445558/\">廣末涼子被捕｜拒配合審訊暴躁大嗌通宵扣查　料今移送地檢署</a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
